'''The Brubeck Institute''' is a special program at the [[University of the Pacific (United States)|University of the Pacific]]'s [[Conservatory of Music, University of the Pacific|Conservatory of Music]]. It was founded in 2000 by noted Jazz pianist and Pacific alum [[Dave Brubeck]].
